    "type": "equipment",
    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><span>This cloak is deep green with a voluminous hood, embroidered with gold trim and symbols significant in elven culture. The cloak allows you to cast the @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.atlgGNI1E1Ox3O3a]{Ghost Sound} cantrip as an arcane innate spell. When you adjust the cloak’s clasp (an Interact action), the cloak transforms to match the environment around you and muffles your sounds, granting you a +1 item bonus to Stealth checks.<br></span></p>\n<p><span><strong>Activate</strong> <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">D</span> Interact; <strong>Frequency</strong> once per day; <strong>Effect</strong> You draw the hood up and gain the effects of @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.XXqE1eY3w3z6xJCB]{Invisibility}, with the spell’s normal duration or until you pull the hood back down, whichever comes first. If you’re also wearing @Compendium[pf2e.equipment-srd.T00Xa9aDwHxd60Zh]{Boots of Elvenkind} you can activate this ability twice per day.</span></p>",
